  "body": "<p>Here in New York for a meeting and quick stopover on my way to Montreal for Crop &amp; Create. Taking advantage of working remotely and having limited supplies with me.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595882466783-KQBM4BZH9ALJZ6JNULDD/11a-Traveler%27s%2BNotebook%2B%2B%2Bhp%2BSprocket.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Got the new <a href=\"http://amzn.to/2dd7UEl\">HP Sprocket</a> and put it to the test on <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/amytangerine/\">my Instagram Story</a>. It's compact and cute and I love a new gadget I can take on-the-go. Thinking I will play with it more and do a thorough review once I get back into the studio. So far it looks like it's an improvement on other Zink printers I have played with. I also love that the prints are stickers! The <a href=\"http://amzn.to/2dd7UEl\">HP Sprocket</a> just came out on September 21 - do any of you have it already and what are your thoughts? Let me know if you have any questions so I can be sure to cover it in the video!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}